{"tid":1043483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶合謀捉人黃腳雞騙財　女友：等我做完先入嚟","createTime":"2019-03-02T10:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T20:05:45.000Z","uid":66271,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5976c9db81e9958b57a751ef41c8137743db6d18","tid":1043483,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:05:22.000Z","msg":"湖北襄陽市一名古姓男子，早前在微信上認識一名周姓女子後，兩人相約以800元（人民幣．下同，約950港元）價格進行性交易；豈料周女早設下「陷阱」，讓張姓男友趁機持刀勒索；好笑的是，周女為減低風險，特意叮嚀男友要待性交易結束後才闖進來。結果古男事後報警，3人一同被拘。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方透露，古男在交易已支付500元（約594港元），在完事後，周女偷偷給張男發短訊，張男隨即持刀闖入內，斥責古男與周女發生關係，再搶走古男1800元（約2139港元）。古男其後不忿損失，便到派出所報案。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員指，周女及張男是有預謀犯罪，已刑事拘留兩人；至於古男亦因嫖娼同被行拘。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737a43ccee46087fb26ecc1d725d120de544194c","tid":1043483,"uid":19360,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da798f59f7c3f14a0c645175a1b72becfc53c7eb","tid":1043483,"uid":163937,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"除晒衫都夠啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b43a37fd848e77cb0c04d21fbfacd1d6539a3c","tid":1043483,"uid":198008,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:12:50.000Z","msg":"為左2千幾蚊比條女人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利害了我的國"},{"pid":"cc85181c0cd3546f7a4ae8c7d05efdf33d34cc67","tid":1043483,"uid":5490,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"真係以客為先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4349446c547f8d6757af16459419f75d236659","tid":1043483,"uid":49336,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":